Invocation Name: the future fourtune
des: Using your Smart Home Alexa, you can ask Alexa to give you a fortune. Shein will scan your voice, and find a fortune that fits you best. There are over 250 fortunes that she can tell you. And every one of them, had a little jazz in them. You can use this to have fun with family and friends. Please enjoy!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
